body.name: Gdrasuya10 34inch Steel Dish Drying Rack Over The Sink, 2 Tier Kitchen Dish Rack with Drainboard Detachable Countertop Dish Drainer Cabinet Utensil Holder Over Sink Cutlery Holder
features: 🍽【High Quality】This dish rack is made of high-quality sturdy steel. The surface of the dish drying rack is covered by black paint, and the thicken steel frames makes the dish drying rack stable and keep dishs safe.

🍽【Mutifunctional】Including a storage basket, a knife rack, a cutting board rack, a utensil holder, are included in this dish drying rack. All the accessories you need are complete, can meet the needs of any kitchenware.

🍽【Cabinet Design】This dish drying rack first layer entirely encloses the second layer, preventing any dust from sticking to dishes and kitchenware. Cabinet has a protective film on the surface, please tear it off before use.
🍽【Measure Your Sink】Please carefully measure 3 numerical values: The width of your kitchen sink, the height of the faucet and the height between the cabinet bottom to the countertop before buying.

🍽【Space Saving】- The size is 37.5*12*31.5 inch, which is very suitable for families of 4-7 people. This dish rack in sink is punched with accurate screw holes, and the screws and hex key come well kept in an extra bag.
body.description: It helps you to save tons of space and keeps your kitchen clean and organized. Different types of cutlery boxes can meet all your need sand you can adjust the removable baskets to your preference.You can also use the rack as a large dish drainer. The counter top will not get wet as water drip directly into the sink.The high quality steel material construction with black-coated finish ensure long lasting durability, no rusting.Sufficient Storage Capacity. Steady and Sturdiness.Powerful 4 suction cups at the foot bottom to protect it from falling or shaking.
